secubox-ksm (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release - KSM memory optimization module.
  * FastAPI backend with sysfs-based KSM control.
  * Endpoints: status, stats, enable, disable, config.
  * P31 Phosphor light theme frontend.
  * Toggle for KSM enable/disable.
  * Sliders for pages_to_scan (100-10000) and sleep_millisecs (10-1000).
  * Memory savings display.

